[Maniema is a province of the Democratic Republic of the Congo. Its capital is Kindu. Maniema is bordered by the provinces of Kasai-Oriental to the west, Orientale to the north, North Kivu and South Kivu to the east, and Katanga to the south. A map of the provinces of Congo DR can be accessed at http://www.mapsofworld.com/democratic-republic-of-congo/democratic-republic-of-congo-political-map.html and a HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/4JoX. - Mod.CP]

