[Rawalpindi is a city in the Pothohar region of Pakistan near the country's capital city of Islamabad, in the province of Punjab. Rawalpindi is the 4th largest city in Pakistan after Karachi, Lahore, and Faisalabad. It can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/1qVK. - Mod.CP]
